  "notes": "Look for more sure thing cards.\n\nDeck Philosophy: No Chase cards because of Gib Remuab (Thrice Hearty Cup of Balder the Red).  Greyhawk World War.\n\nNote: Chase card=card number ending in \"of 20\" or \"of 25\"\n\nCombos:\n-A Good Defense + Mebhaigl Surge or Jerome to retrieve offensive spells.\n-Servants of Faith + Elemental Swarm\n\nPlay tips:\n-Reincarnate to bring Gib Remuab or Jerome into play.\n-Have Kiri raze realms and cast disintegrate/estate transference from discards instead of spoils.  Or have her retrieve rule card and put it back into play.\n\nChamps: Wizard and Cleric Casters.  Many clerics for discarding to bring out Lady of Fate.  Good battle powers.\n-Spellfire Citadel + Ancient Arms of the Shield Lands = unraze extra realms each turn\n\nWizard & Cleric Spells:\nFocus on spells that will win in battle so Rule Spell Book of Drawmij can keep them in play.",
